---

## 🖥️ Supported CPUs

EcoTrace automatically detects TDP values using the [Boavizta](https://github.com/Boavizta/cpu-spec) database with 1800+ CPUs:

- Intel Core i3 / i5 / i7 / i9 (all generations)
- AMD Ryzen 3 / 5 / 7 / 9
- Apple M1 / M2 / M3
- AMD Threadripper, EPYC
- Intel Xeon

